OL,3,CLiverpool captain Virgil van Dijk says
OL,4,Che is 'dreading' Klopp exit
OL,6,FThe defender spoke with ITV News'
OL,7,FSports Editor Steve Scott about
OL,8,Fchasing silverware, his advice for
OL,9,FKlopp's successor and supporting young
OL,10,Ftalent
OL,12,Fcaptain says he is "dreading" Jurgen
OL,13,FKlopp's departure from Anfield at the
OL,14,Fend of the season.
OL,16,F"I'm a very emotional person and I
OL,17,Fdon't like to say goodbyes," he told
OL,18,FITV News.
