OL,3,CLiverpool captain Virgil van Dijk says
OL,4,Che is 'dreading' Klopp exit
OL,6,F"Being the captain now as well, it's
OL,7,Fgoing to be horrible in that sense,
OL,8,Fbecause probably I'll have to speak a
OL,9,Flittle bit, and like I said - that day
OL,10,FI'll be dreading... It makes it a lot
OL,11,Feasier if we have success."
OL,13,Fannounced his bombshell decision to
OL,14,Fleave the club earlier this year.
OL,16,FVan Dijk was appointed captain by the
OL,17,FGerman manager last summer, and the
OL,18,Ftwo have a close relationship.
OL,20,F"It's not only the bosses leaving,"
OL,21,Fvan Dijk said.
