OL,4,Che is 'dreading' Klopp exit
OL,6,F"It's going to be a lot of changes and
OL,7,Fmore staff leaving... It will be a
OL,8,Ftough day, but until the day that
OL,9,Fwe'll fight and be positive and put
OL,10,Fall our focus into that to be
OL,11,Fpositive."
OL,13,FLiverpool are top of the Premier
OL,14,FLeague with nine games left to play,
OL,15,Ftwo points ahead of Arsenal and three
OL,16,Fin front of champions Manchester City,
OL,17,Fwho are competing for their fourth
OL,18,Fconsecutive title.
OL,20,FBoth of Liverpool's league rivals are
OL,21,Fin action on Wednesday evening.
