OL,3,CLiverpool captain Virgil van Dijk says
OL,4,Che is 'dreading' Klopp exit
OL,6,F"We know the end of the season will be
OL,7,Femotional. But we can make it
OL,8,Femotional in a good way by winning
OL,9,Ftrophies," van Dijk said.
OL,11,FAsked what success for Liverpool would
OL,12,Flook like this season, he added:
OL,13,F"Winning the two remaining trophies,
OL,14,Fthat is success.
OL,16,F"The only influence we have is the
OL,17,Fgames that we play... We have to
OL,18,Fembrace it, we have to enjoy it, we
OL,19,Fhave to go out there and fight."
