OL,3,CLiverpool captain Virgil van Dijk says
OL,4,Che is 'dreading' Klopp exit
OL,6,FLiverpool lost to Manchester United in
OL,7,Fthe final of the FA Cup last month but
OL,8,Fcould still win the Europa League and
OL,9,Fthe Premier League.
OL,11,FNo matter how the Reds perform in the
OL,12,Fremainder of the season, following in
OL,13,Fthe footsteps of the charismatic and
OL,14,Fmuch-loved Klopp will be a daunting
OL,15,Fprospect, but whoever gets that job
OL,16,Fmay just get a helping hand.
