OL,6,FVan Dijk's contract expires in 2025
OL,7,Fand his future at Liverpool had been
OL,8,Fquestioned after he admitted he
OL,9,F"didn't know" whether he'd play under
OL,10,FKlopp's successor earlier this year.
OL,12,FBut despite being linked to a move
OL,13,Faway from Anfield, van Dijk indicated
OL,14,Fto ITV News that he's staying put,
OL,15,Fmore than suggesting he'll still be
OL,16,Faround when the new boss takes charge.
